Day two of the Big Brother Naija Season Seven saw 12 new housemates join the already unveiled twelve making a total of twenty four housemates. The new twelve housemates were however separated from the first set from day one opening. Here are the first 12 Housemates for the current edition. Bella Believes people would want to watch the season seven edition because of her while assuring that she is the life of the party. Eloswag A dancer and artist, Elowag promises to bring all the energy and enthusiasm. “I am the next level because entertainment na me” he said. Doyin Ondo state born and a medical radiographer. The world revolves around me and even if it doesn’t it should because I am the next level. Adekunle A Lagos island born, a little bit calm but and at the same time a handful. Allysyn I am different, very unique and open minded.   Buhari celebrates Amusan, Brume over World Athletics feats     FCT taskforce begins massive demolition of…     Property destroyed as fire razes two-storey in Onitsha   Dotun Has the right energy and ready to go. Chomzy Vibes, energy and swag Giddyfia Contagious cruise and vibe Diana I am going to give it to them hot hot. Hermes He is certain that he would win fans because he’s brining every aspect of who he is into the house. Chichi A striper. She’s bringing her truth and the real stripper vibes. Sheggz A professional footballer. I am me, I keep it real.